author: Disney
description:
D23 Gold Members are invited to a dazzling evening at the virtual D23 Gold Theater presented by State Farm during “Magic After Dark: The Story of Disney’s Nighttime Spectaculars”. The nighttime spectaculars at Disney Parks have created treasured memories for guests for decades, providing their “kiss goodnight” after a day of Disney fun. In this D23 Gold Theater presentation, hosts Jessica McDonald from D23 and producer and Disney author Graham Allan look back at the fan-favorite “Magic After Dark” panel from D23: The Ultimate Disney Fan Event last August. Our hosts will also take a peek at what’s to come, as they give fans an exclusive look at new shows bringing the night to life this summer at Disneyland and Walt Disney World! 

Join us on Thursday, May 29, 2025, at 5 p.m. PT / 8 p.m. ET for the latest installment of D23 Gold Theater.  

Can’t make the show? We will have an encore airing on Saturday, May 31, 2025, at 11 a.m. PT / 2 p.m. ET.
